title: Match History not working

There's a known bug with the match history page that prevents it from loading for some players. If none of the potential workarounds I linked in the thread you referenced worked for you, then you're encountering the bug. There are no known workarounds other than the ones I posted in that discussion (clear cache, disable add-ons, another browser).

Let me know if you have any other questions.

Thanks for the response.  That is very unfortunate though and I like reviewing my matches. :-(  Seems to be that I just can't access that JavaScript file (on my connection I guess?) for whatever reason.  I have Verizon FIOS if that helps.  I also cannot hit that page on my phone (Verizon as well).  My friend can't load it either (on Cox Communications).

Any idea on when this will be fixed?  Anything other info I could provide that would be useful?

I cannot provide an ETA on the fix, as I don't have that information. We're aware of the issue and have been investigating, so additional information is not necessary.

Let me know if there's anything else I can help you with.
